  System.* Communications of the ACM, 1978.
- Ghorbal, K., Goubault, E., & Putot, S. *The Zonotope Abstract Domain.*
  SAS, 2009.
- Singh, G. et al. *An Abstract Domain for Certifying Neural Networks.*
  POPL, 2019. (DeepZ / DeepPoly)
- Girard, A. *Reachability of Uncertain Linear Systems Using Zonotopes.*
  HSCC, 2005.
- Kocsis, L. & Szepesvári, C. *Bandit Based Monte-Carlo Planning.* ECML, 2006.
- Kwiatkowska, M. et al. *PRISM-games: Verification and Strategy Synthesis for
  Stochastic Multi-Player Games.* TACAS, 2020.
- Alshiekh, M. et al. *Safe Reinforcement Learning via Shielding.* AAAI, 2018.
- Serebryany, K. & Iskhodzhanov, T. *ThreadSanitizer — Data Race Detection in
  Practice.* WBIA, 2009.
- Blackshear, S. et al. *RacerD: Compositional Static Race Detection.*
  OOPSLA, 2018.

